Interface Log

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
All Known Implementing Classes:
Log_$logger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="ISPN") @ValidIdRange(min=8001, max=9000) public interface Log extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
Log abstraction for the JDBC cache store.
